==== Decade 2010- ====
In [[2009<U+2013>10 Cypriot First Division]] was relagated again in second division. In [[2010<U+2013>11 Cypriot Second Division]] ensured the promotion in first division. In [[2011<U+2013>12 Cypriot First Division]], finished in 7th place.

