==Nea Salamina in CFA competitions==
=== Overall statistics on class A ===
The table below shows the overall progress of Nea Salamina in [[Cypriot First Division]] from 1955 to 2012. The score is the sum of the actual score of each period, regardless of the scoring system. Using the modern scoring system (Win = 3 points, Draw = 1 point, Loss: 0 points) the score is 1600 points. The period [[1963-64 Cypriot First Division|1963-64]], in which the championship was interrupted, not included.

