==Nea Salamina in Cypriot Cup==
Nea Salamis has 56 entries in the Cyprus Cup, having one win, three appearances in the final, semi-final appearances in 12 and 32 appearances in the quarter-finals. The table below shows the statistics of Nea Salamina for all cup matches in Cyprus (1953/1954-2012/2013) per opponent.

